{"tid":1543074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府今日已經開始通過不同方式向海外宣傳","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:13:21.000Z","uid":57891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d6eb13844e2b389a8769098571b22a2f42119025","tid":1543074,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCRojZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCRojZu.jpg&h=a7e87244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府在澳洲報章登廣告宣傳香港<br />\n05.09.2019 10:02<br />\n特區政府今日在《澳洲金融時報》刊登全版廣告，強調香港依然安全，一定會重新恢復。廣告指外國社會可能看到和聽到很多有關香港示威情況，不過很多在社交媒體被「分享」的內容，只是香港複雜的社會、經濟及政治事件的其中一塊拼圖，特區政府需要時間處理問題，並決心以和平、理性及合理的方法解決。<br />\n<br />\n廣告又指，特區政府遵循「一國兩制」，港人繼續享有和平示威的權利，但政府不會容許暴力，目前香港經濟表現仍維持強勁，繼續是開放的國際大都會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1165010&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1165010%26csid%3D261_341&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=52d1f3d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1165010&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"cc91d91539456812fb907b340eb7eaf1ccd883a6","tid":1543074,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi